r>Czakoriah <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ugorebloodlust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gore Bloodlust</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.clicksmilie.de/sammlung/waffen/waffen057.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Dead Sexy Leezard</span><br>  Posts: 511<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/15/02 7:14:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2542.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: “The Masters” Tournament  (Level 60 ONLY) </span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> A 100 platinum per participant registration fee is required (90% of registration fee goes to award the Champions and 10% is retained by the promoter.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br><br>A true test of champions is fine, but I see this as just a scam to fill you pocket. I dislike how this first came across.<br><br> <p><br>Gore Bloodlust<br>60th Iksar Warlord ( Dead Sexy )<br>Guild Leader of <a href="http://pub64.ezboard.com/blustforblood">Lust for Blood</a><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67224">My Stuff</a><br>Life, Liberty, and the pursuit of all who threaten it.<br>Only the dead have seen the end of war.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uczakoriah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Czakoriah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/15/02 7:33:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2542.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: “The Masters” Tournament  (Level 60 ONLY) </span><hr size=1> Come on Gore, How much you think I am going to make off of this....20 players show up that is 2000 plat I keep 1/10th of it that is 200 plat of which I will be giving all to my guild for their assistance in this.  Is it a scam to want to host something that is going to be a specticle to seethat really ripping people off?  I could be up in the Bazaar trying to rip people off that way but no, I figure I can promote some fun on this server and help my guild out at the same time.  Sorry if you feel that way, cause it wasn't intended to rip off the level 60s, and how quickly could a level 60 make 100 plat in one kill?  Geez this is what I get for taking time out and trying to promote some fun on this server, and trying to make a little coin for my guild in the process.  I did this because you were wondering on the another post why the Arena event I/Northern Elite was sponsoring was only for the Fellowship.  I figured well why not host an event for the high end players to enjoy.  Hell I want to see you if you are all that you are talked up to be, why not host something and find out.  Sorry I am not donating my time for your enjoyment, I really didn't think 10 plat per person is ripping someone off for running an event that provides 2-3 hours of player enjoyment.  I guess there will be no more after this one.<br><br>Czakoriah<br><br>  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/utiestooakey.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tiesto Oakey</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Shadowknight who says Ni!</span><br>  Posts: 287<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/15/02 8:59:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2542.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: “The Masters” Tournament  (Level 60 ONLY) </span><hr size=1> Can I come at 58 (probably