=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: “The Masters” Tournament  (Level 60s ONLY) </span><hr size=1> You know what...screw it!  Since some people are uptight about the money issue I have modified the money distribution...<br><br>The entire 100 plat will be rewarded back to the champions, and the Promoter will graciously accept, on behalf of his guild the Northern Elite, any donations for providing this event for the players.<br><br>Czakoriah <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usumataitherogue.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SumataiTheRogue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 130<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/15/02 11:43:58 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2542.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: “The Masters” Tournament  (Level 60 ONLY) </span><hr size=1> QUOTE:<br>&quot;A true test of champions is fine, but I see this as just a scam to fill you pocket. I dislike how this first came across.&quot;<br><br>What, someone can't come up with an idea, organize an event, and make a little change?  You know how hard it is to organize an event.  What, should he just quit his life to just organize things for the enjoyment of others?<br><br>Plus, what is 100pp to someone who is 60?  Let's see....1/30th of a nice drop in Velks?<br><br>I applaud Czak for his efforts.  The reason Gore dislikes it, is because he wasn't invited to the first one.  Gore, I'm not trying to flame you but if you don't like the idea, graciously decline.  People charge for lots of things, why not an event.  It's not the first time...and surely won't be the last.<br><br>Sumatai <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=ti